PRWebDistributionData.Headline: Now, this is a story all about how My life got flipped-turned upside down
PRWebDistributionData.Summary: And I would like to take a minute Just sit right there and think what to say to get more that 80 chars.
PRWebDistributionData.Body: In west Philadelphia born and raised On the playground was where I spent most of my days Chillin out maxin relaxin all cool And all shootin some b-ball outside of the school When a couple of guys who were up to no good Started making trouble in my neighborhood I got in one little fight and my mom got scared She said Youre movin with your auntie and uncle in Bel Air
